title: can't get through to EDD office
text: Is everyone else just getting a machine that tells you to fill out an application online and then hangs up? I have income from multiple states and so my options are to fax in my application or call and speak to a representative. I tried faxing in an application and waited the 10 days for a response but I didn't get anything... so I was hoping to check on the status or file again through the phone but nothing.
